">（</span><span type="rt">しつ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>に<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">入</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">はい</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ってあたりを<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">見</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">み</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>まわしました。<lb />
